text: Kiuruvesi is a town in Northern Savonia, Finland. As of 28 February 2023, 7,578 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Iisalmi, Pielavesi, Pyhäjärvi, Pyhäntä and Vieremä. == Other websites == * Town of Kiuruvesi – Official website Category:Municipalities of North Savo Category:Towns in Finland
